  <section class="intro">
    <p>Hi, I’m Tatiana Yasmine Adriano Boccone (aka Tati / Yasmi) — a Filipino-American creative with over 7 years of experience translating ideas into design through video editing, campaign execution, and content design. I’m passionate about motion design and love crafting compelling brand narratives using tools like Adobe Creative Suite, Figma &lt;3, and Final Cut Pro.</p>
  </section>

